steps.html_instructions: At the roundabout, take the 1st exit

At the roundabout, take the 1st exit
At the roundabout, take the 4th exit
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for Valencia and merge onto AP-7
Take exit 11 for N-344 toward La Font de la Figuera/Alicante/Alacant/Murcia

Continue onto N-344/A-33
Continue to follow A-33
Take exit 601B to merge onto RM-2 toward Mazarrón/Fuente Álamo/Cartagena
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto RM-23 heading to Mazarrón
Take the exit on the left onto RM-3 toward Mazarrón
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Calle Cueva del Pelciego
Continue onto Calle Sierra de la Torrecilla
